\\*\\*This is a remote, contractual position\\*\\*


The editorial team at TheSportster.com is currently looking for contributors to produce
**wrestling list articles**
for the site.


**Who We Are**
TheSportster is a trusted resource covering timely news and interesting facts from the world of pro wrestling (WWE, AEW, and more.)


**Expectations**

* A minimum of 5 articles per week;
* Work under reasonable deadlines and submitting tasks on time;
* Report to Lead Editor and implement feedback efficiently;
* Finding and resizing images to fit the websites guidelines;
* Following formatting and link guides;
* Making revisions as requested by the editorial team

**What We’re Looking For**

* Excellent research skills - we do not accept plagiarism of any kind;
* Broad knowledge of pro wrestling;
* Relevant experience writing wrestling content for a sports publication

We will get back to you as soon as possible if we think you'd make a solid addition to the team.


